meta.title: Nate Goes Back to the Year 2000 and meets Caillou

ttsdata.text: So let me get this straight? Nicks going to go through this scanner, scan his brain to get mind power to create enough charge for this conveyer machine to suck me into.
The year 2000, so I can grab enough water for the Super Duper Mart? Are you guys crazy. Why the year 2000?
As I've explained over 3 times. We need a date that doesn't have any historical impact of war or protest, so nobody in the time period will think of you as suspisious.
The year 2000, isn't considered a notable time period. Wow.
Hey, I wouldn't anger the lady, shes got more bolts in her than my entire cercuit breaker does.
Look, just get in the fucking machine, I'll do the work. You just gotta lay and act pretty.
Hey, I have to go to the bathroom.
Ha ha, very funny.
Hum, I appear to be in someones house. Looks pretty modern for the year 2000.
I guess I'll take a look around for an exit.
Something smells good
Oh shit! A family, I gotta hide.
Perfect, the pie came out delicious looking.
What? Huh? What in gods name is this?
Hey KAI U. guess what day today it is.
Oh boy. Caillou's Special Treat Day? Red Rocket Candy Day? Chuck E Cheese's Pizza Day?
No! None of those stupid imaginary holidays you came up with was even close.
Today is thanksgiving, you know, the holiday you learned in kindergarten with Miss Martin. We have a bunch of food on the table that you'll enjoy.
Oh yeah! I remember it. It's where those people in feathers attacked the people who wore black hats. They look so weird looking. Wah wah wah wah.
KAI U, you are being very racist. Do not ruin this dinner with racist jokes. Your grandma and grandpa will be here soon. Behave now!
Grandma and grandpa? Yay! They're going to give me lots of kisses and lots of treats soon. This will finally be a great day!
Sweety? Can you help me with this? Aw, shit. Boris, can you get the door? I think it's grandma and grandpa.
Just a minute!
KAI U, I am fucking warning you, if you ask grandma and grandpa for any treats then I will burn every toy you own! Do not blow this!
Yes daddy, I won't ask for anything.
Maybe I can see if I can help out this bald little kid.
Oh hi. Wait. Hey you? Yeah you? Are you one of my family members?
Um, yeah. I'm one of your uncles.
Oh, then you might be one of the creepy uncles in my dads basement. Anyway, I got a question for you. Do you have any treats? Candy? Some gumdrops at all?
Nah, I don't got any.
Well. My grandma has some treats on her. But I would have to steal them. Hey, maybe you can steal them from my grandmothers purse then put them in my toy chest.
Sure thing. But, for a price that is.
Don't worry, I know what money is. If you do it then I can give you 5 bucks from my piggy bank.
Deal.
Okay dad, football time. Let's see if gary tucker can throw them eagles back to philly.
Oh ho ho, oh that's a good one. Well they been at it for years, but this last time might be the breaking point.
Oh, I'm just so hungry all the time.
Quiet. I'm trying to hear.
Now I think they had some toast hidden in here for me to munch on.
What's this? A ginger bread man from. When's this say? 1994?
Well it's mine now.
That's weird. It felt like someone grabbed my pants.
That little bald kid said to put the candy in a toy chest?
Ah, there.
Now to get my 5 bucks.
Hey. KAI U.
HEY! Did you get the candy, is it in my toy box?
Yup. All locked tight for a little 6 year old to eat and have the time of his life.
Thanks, santa claus
Hey KAI U, it's time for some yummy turkey. Come to the dining room.
Yuck! I hate turkey. I wish I could have pizza from chuck e cheeses. Ugh, this is going to be the worst day of my entire life.
Who is that guy in the blue jump suit? Is it Doris's brother? I've never met him.
Yay! Treats!
